seo.title: We're now open in India! - FLS
seo.metaDesc: We are expanding our global footprint with a new office - FLS India, where our handpicked, local experts create bespoke, world-class supply chain solutions for you.
seo.opengraphTitle: We're now open in India! - FLS
seo.opengraphDescription: We are expanding our global footprint with a new office - FLS India, where our handpicked, local experts create bespoke, world-class supply chain solutions for you.

blocks.name: core/paragraph
blocks.saveContent: We are expanding our global footprint with a new office in India. Strategically located in Chennai, the second largest container port in the country, FLS India is where our handpicked, local experts create bespoke, world-class supply chain solutions for you. This opening is another part of our continual growth in providing Tailor-Made Global Solutions beyond scale, geography, and industry.

blocks.name: core/paragraph
blocks.saveContent: The FLS India office will be headed by Nataraj Ganapathy, who has been our Overseas Delegate and now Branch Manager - Chennai, along with M Ramesh, Airfreight Product Manager.

blocks.name: core/paragraph
blocks.saveContent: By choosing this particular location, we are making another step towards our brand promise to keep the world moving, integrating the Indian subcontinent into our strong FLS network in Asia and beyond. Marcel Kirschnick, Director, FLS Logistics, shared about this momentous event.
